description:
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will be expected to undertake a range of secretarial and administrative duties, be highly organised and should have the ability to plan and prioritise their workload, work to strict deadlines and use their own initiative.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be the main point of contact for all queries into the Division directing calls as appropriate. The role involves a significant amount of meetings administration as well as providing personal assistant service to the 3 Divisional Directors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will be expected to work flexibly to meet the needs of the Service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Helen Brislen (Directorate Manager) helen.brislen@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;0151 678 5111 Ext 7990&lt;/p&gt;
